Package: infoxtr
Title: Information-Theoretic Measures for Revealing Variable Interactions
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Wenbo", family = "Lyu",
           email = "lyu.geosocial@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-6003-3800"))
Description: Implements information-theoretic measures to explore variable interactions, including KSG-based mutual information estimation for continuous variables, Knockoff Conditional Mutual Information (KOCMI, doi:...), Synergistic-Unique-Redundant Decomposition (SURD, Martinez-Sanchez et al., 2024, doi:10.1038/s41467-024-53373-4), allowing detection of complex and diverse relationships among variables.
